name: TON-Blind Follower/Point Of View CD
description:
TON "Blind Follower/Point of View" Re-issue 

Fresh Blood Management:

One of best records from Ohio Death Metal band TON, originally released in 1998. Taken from 2 demos compiled on one CD, "Blind Follower/Point of View" contains lots of groove and ear pounding riffs makes this disc one of the heaviest Brutal Death Metal albums.

The original "Blind Follower/Point of View" CD has totally 9 tracks, the re-issue version comes with a new  design and 1 additional track taken from the bands previous demo, "Crushing Design".

The re-issue of TON "Blind Follower/Point of View" CD limited to 500 copies and won't be pressed again. 

Highly recommended for die hard fans of ENTORTUREMENT, DYING FETUS, (old) SUFFOCATION and DEHUMANIZED! So, what are you waiting for? Get a copy of one of the best album in 90's!
